# Project Description

Soro Finance is a accounting and payment automation platform designed for decentralized teams. It helps projects track their income and expenses, manage recurring payments, and automate on-chain and off-chain transactions.

## Key features include:

Expense & Income Tracking with reporting capabilities
Automated & Manual Payments via predefined rules
Token Conversions for seamless treasury management
Expense Requests & Approvals for team-based operations
Comprehensive Reporting & Data Export

Soro Finance aims to simplify financial management for blockchain-based projects, ensuring transparency, automation, and efficient fund distribution.
